{
    "componentChunkName": "component---src-templates-blog-template-js",
    "path": "/about-dev-setting/",
    "result": {"data":{"cur":{"id":"6aa7bccc-91cd-5fa8-8292-6d2609116fa8","html":"<p>주니어 개발자(나)에게 ‘입사하고 힘들었던 경험이 있나요?’ 라고 물으면 반은 ‘개발 환경 세팅이요!’ 할 것 같다. 개발 공부를 하면서 노트북을 바꿔 총 3번 환경 세팅을 한 경험이 있다. 그때마다 느낀점은 블로그를 잘 찾아야한다. 컴퓨터마다 사양이 다르고 M1칩이 나오면서 세팅 방법이 다양해졌다. 이번에 블로깅할 세팅 방법은 Mac Pro Inter에 적용한 방법이다.</p>\n<p>아래 문서에서 많은 도움을 받았다. 대부분 Mac 세팅에 대해 정리가 잘 되어있다.</p>\n<p>📖 <a href=\"https://subicura.com/mac/\">macOS 안내서</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://subicura.com/mac/dev/\">개발 환경 설정</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"개발-환경-세팅-xcode-설치한-상태\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C-%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD-%EC%84%B8%ED%8C%85-xcode-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98%ED%95%9C-%EC%83%81%ED%83%9C\" aria-label=\"개발 환경 세팅 xcode 설치한 상태 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>개발 환경 세팅 (Xcode 설치한 상태)</h3>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://brew.sh/index_ko\">Homebrew</a> 설치</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">brew install node</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">npm install -g node@version --force</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">npm install -g npm@version</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">npm install yarn</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">vim ~/.zshrc</code></li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">NVM_DIR</span><span class=\"token operator\">=~</span>/.nvm\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">source</span> <span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span>brew --prefix nvm<span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>/nvm.sh</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"7\">\n<li>esc → :wq → enter</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">source ~/.zshrc</code></li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"vscode\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#vscode\" aria-label=\"vscode permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>VScode</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> cask\n$ brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> --cask visual-studio-code</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"git-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#git-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"git 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Git 설정</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> <span class=\"token function\">git</span> git-lfs\n\n$ <span class=\"token function\">git</span> lfs <span class=\"token function\">install</span>\n$ <span class=\"token function\">git</span> config --global user.name <span class=\"token string\">\"Your Name\"</span>\n$ <span class=\"token function\">git</span> config --global user.email <span class=\"token string\">\"you@your-domain.com\"</span>\n$ <span class=\"token function\">git</span> config --global core.precomposeunicode <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>\n$ <span class=\"token function\">git</span> config --global core.quotepath <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>ref. <a href=\"https://herojoon-dev.tistory.com/50\">https://herojoon-dev.tistory.com/50</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"watchman-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#watchman-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"watchman 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>watchman 설치</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>vscode 편집기 변경된 내용 자동 탐지하는 기능 (Native 시 필요)</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> watchman\n$ watchman --version</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"react-native-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#react-native-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"react native 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>React Native 설정</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://reactnative.dev/docs/environment-setup\">공식문서</a> 참고</p>\n<h3 id=\"android-studio-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#android-studio-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"android studio 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Android studio 설정</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Java11 설치 (<a href=\"https://soongjamm.tistory.com/104\">https://soongjamm.tistory.com/104</a>)</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ brew tap AdoptOpenJDK/openjdk\n$ brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> adoptopenjdk11 --cask</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>자바 버전 및 경로 확인</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ /usr/libexec/java_home -V\nMatching Java Virtual Machines <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>:\n    <span class=\"token number\">14.0</span>.1, x86_64:    <span class=\"token string\">\"OpenJDK 14.0.1\"</span>    /Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/openjdk-14.0.1.jdk/Contents/Home\n    <span class=\"token number\">11.0</span>.9.1, x86_64:    <span class=\"token string\">\"AdoptOpenJDK 11\"</span>    /Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/adoptopenjdk-11.jdk/Contents/Home\n    <span class=\"token number\">1.8</span>.0_221, x86_64:    <span class=\"token string\">\"Java SE 8\"</span>    /Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/jdk1.8.0_221.jdk/Contents/Home\n\n/Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/openjdk-14.0.1.jdk/Contents/Home</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>./zshrc 파일 마지막 줄에 아래 코드 삽입 후 저장</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">JAVA_8_HOME</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/jdk1.8.0_221.jdk/Contents/Home\"</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">JAVA_11_HOME</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/adoptopenjdk-11.jdk/Contents/Home\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">alias</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">java8</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'export JAVA_HOME=$JAVA_8_HOME'</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">alias</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">java11</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'export JAVA_HOME=$JAVA_11_HOME'</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">source</span> .zshrc\n$ java --version\nopenjdk version <span class=\"token string\">\"11.0.9.1\"</span> <span class=\"token number\">2020</span>-11-04\nOpenJDK Runtime Environment AdoptOpenJDK <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>build <span class=\"token number\">11.0</span>.9.1+1<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nOpenJDK <span class=\"token number\">64</span>-Bit Server VM AdoptOpenJDK <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>build <span class=\"token number\">11.0</span>.9.1+1, mixed mode<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.android.com/studio?hl=es-419\">Android studio</a> 다운로드</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://dev-yakuza.posstree.com/ko/react-native/install-on-mac/#%EC%95%88%EB%93%9C%EB%A1%9C%EC%9D%B4%EB%93%9C-%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%9C%EB%94%94%EC%98%A4-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\">Android studio 설정</a></li>\n<li>환경 변수 설정 (<code class=\"language-text\">.zshrc</code> 파일 아래 코드 삽입 후 저장)</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># export ANDROID_SDK_ROOT=/Users/siyoonjeon/Library/Android/sdk</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">ANDROID_SDK_ROOT</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>your <span class=\"token environment constant\">HOME</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>/Library/Android/sdk\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\"><span class=\"token environment constant\">PATH</span></span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token environment constant\">$PATH</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span><span class=\"token variable\">$ANDROID_SDK_ROOT</span>/emulator\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\"><span class=\"token environment constant\">PATH</span></span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token environment constant\">$PATH</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span><span class=\"token variable\">$ANDROID_SDK_ROOT</span>/tools\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\"><span class=\"token environment constant\">PATH</span></span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token environment constant\">$PATH</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span><span class=\"token variable\">$ANDROID_SDK_ROOT</span>/tools/bin\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\"><span class=\"token environment constant\">PATH</span></span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token environment constant\">$PATH</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span><span class=\"token variable\">$ANDROID_SDK_ROOT</span>/platform-tools</code></pre></div>\n<p>주소를 모를 경우 안드로이드 스튜디오 setting > android <code class=\"language-text\">SDK</code> 내에서 확인 가능</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.android.com/filetransfer/\">Android File Transfer 다운로드</a></li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C-%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD-%EC%84%B8%ED%8C%85-xcode-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98%ED%95%9C-%EC%83%81%ED%83%9C\">개발 환경 세팅 (Xcode 설치한 상태)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#vscode\">VScode</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#git-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\">Git 설정</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#watchman-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\">watchman 설치</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#react-native-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\">React Native 설정</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#android-studio-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\">Android studio 설정</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>","excerpt":"주니어 개발자(나)에게 ‘입사하고 힘들었던 경험이 있나요?’ 라고 물으면 반은 ‘개발 환경 세팅이요!’ 할 것 같다. 개발 공부를 하면서 노트북을 바꿔 총 3번 환경 세팅을 한 경험이 있다. 그때마다 느낀점은 블로그를 잘 찾아야한다. 컴퓨터마다 사양이 다르고 M1칩이 나오면서 세팅 방법이 다양해졌다. 이번에 블로깅할 세팅 방법은 Mac Pro Inter에 적용한 방법이다. 아래 문서에서 많은 도움을 받았다. 대부분 Mac 세팅에 대해 정리가 잘 되어있다. 📖 macOS 안내서 개발 환경 설정 개발 환경 세팅 (Xcode 설치한 상태) Homebrew 설치      esc → :wq → enter  VScode Git 설정 ref. https://herojoon-dev.tistory.com/50 watchman 설치 vscode 편집기 변경된 내용 자동 탐지하는 기능 (Native 시 필요) React Native 설정 공식문서 참고 Android studio 설정 Java11 설치…","frontmatter":{"date":"December 23, 2021","title":"개발 환경 세팅","categories":"blog","author":"Siyoon Jeon","emoji":"🛠"},"fields":{"slug":"/about-dev-setting/"}},"next":null,"prev":{"id":"8a661c57-0f0c-5178-8905-c0bfc88ac124","html":"<h3 id=\"commint-lint\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#commint-lint\" aria-label=\"commint lint permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Commint Lint</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>커밋하기전에 바뀐 부분에 대해 lint 검사 통과해야 작성 가능</li>\n<li>@commitlint를 사용해서 해당 commit title만 커밋이 가능</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"husky\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#husky\" aria-label=\"husky permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Husky</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>프론트엔드 개발 환경에서 git hook를 쉽게 제어할 수 있도록 해주는 매니저</li>\n<li>즉, <strong>eslint가 깨지면 commit 자체를 막는 방법</strong></li>\n<li>commit 시, commit 자체를 막고 어디가 잘못되었는지 표시해줌</li>\n<li>리뷰 시, lint에 대한 부분을 고려하지 않아 코드에 집중할 수 있다는 장점이 있음.</li>\n<li>반면, husky만 적용할 때에 모든 파일을 모두 commit마다 검사하여 시간이 오래걸린다는 단점이 존재함.</li>\n<li>이에 <a href=\"https://www.notion.so/b64b9ddd79e5472cb2b9813d669bcd6e\">lint-staged</a>를 사용하여 스테이지에 올라온 파일만 검사하도록 보완함.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"git-hook\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#git-hook\" aria-label=\"git hook permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Git Hook</h3>\n<p>git을 쓰다가 특정 이벤트(commit, push 등)가 벌어졌을 때, 그 순간 ‘갈고리’를 걸어 스트립트가 실행되도록 도와주는 것</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 12.222222222222221%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAiklEQVQI1zXMQQ7BQBiA0V6fdNFwAWlcQWm7o0GsCBuKpUFanbYz/7D6BHGA97xk+yKIHZdScEZzVpZuJMz3Qv2407SGMBMGU0vdGMRolrnQGQlH9TEVqjAEsSVaO7x096SXOtQ/vFr8sbA4CFVxQ+uaYWYJZ+abS6tZ5YIfCSf1M6o09BPLZON4A2L6j5oak3rOAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"githook\"\n        title=\"githook\"\n        src=\"/static/46cfb157977ec3efbc0718396767acca/37523/githook.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/46cfb157977ec3efbc0718396767acca/e9ff0/githook.png 180w,\n/static/46cfb157977ec3efbc0718396767acca/f21e7/githook.png 360w,\n/static/46cfb157977ec3efbc0718396767acca/37523/githook.png 720w,\n/static/46cfb157977ec3efbc0718396767acca/2e367/githook.png 1066w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Git Hook 단계별 특성\n<ul>\n<li><strong>pre-commit</strong> : 커밋 메세지를 작성하기 전에 호출된다.</li>\n<li>prepare-commit-msg : 커밋 메세지와 관련된 명령을 넣을 때 호출된다.</li>\n<li>commit-msg : 커밋 메세지와 관련된 명령을 넣을 때 호출된다.</li>\n<li>post-commit : 커밋이 완료되면 호출된다.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"version\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#version\" aria-label=\"version permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Version</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>v4 : package.json 또는 .huskyrc 파일을 최상위 경로에 만들어서 관리</li>\n<li>v7 : git hook shell 스크립트를 작성하여 .exe 파일을 생성해주듯 해당 프로젝트에 적용</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\">## 업데이트 4 to 7</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> husky@latest --save-dev <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> npx husky-init <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">exec</span> -- github:typicode/husky-4-to-7 --remove-v4-config\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">## init 과정에서 7.0.0 버전으로 다운그레이드 되기 때문</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> husky@latest --save-dev</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># .husky/commit-msg (v7)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">#!/bin/sh</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">.</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token function\">dirname</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$0</span>\"</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>/_/husky.sh\"</span>\n\nnpx --no-install commitlint --edit <span class=\"token variable\">$1</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># .husky/pre-commit (v7)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">#!/bin/sh</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">.</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token function\">dirname</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$0</span>\"</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>/_/husky.sh\"</span>\n\nnpx lint-staged</code></pre></div>\n<p>📖  <a href=\"https://typicode.github.io/husky/#/\">Husky 공식문서</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"lint-staged\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#lint-staged\" aria-label=\"lint staged permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>lint-staged</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>stage상태의 git 파일에 대해서만 lint와 설정해둔 명령어를 실행해주는 라이브러리</li>\n<li>git add로 커밋 대상이 된 상태인 stage 상태라고 함.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"version-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#version-1\" aria-label=\"version 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Version</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> lint-staged@12.1.4</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token comment\">//.lintstagedrc</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"*.{js,jsx,ts,tsx}\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"eslint\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>📖 <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/lint-staged\">lint-staged</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"commitlint\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#commitlint\" aria-label=\"commitlint permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>@commitlint</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>커밋 메세지에 대해서 lint를 할 수 있게 해주는 툴</li>\n<li>깔끔한 커밋 메세지로 유지 보수에 큰 도움이 되는 장점이 있음.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"version-2\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#version-2\" aria-label=\"version 2 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Version</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>@commitlint/cli <strong>v15.0.0</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>v16 일부 프로젝트에서 ts 오류가 발생함 → 전체 commitlint v15로 다운그레이드</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>@commitlint/config-conventional <strong>v.16.0.0</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> uninstall @commitlint/cli @commitlint/config-conventional\n<span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> @commitlint/cli@15 --save-dev\n<span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> @commitlint/config-conventional@latest --save-dev</code></pre></div>\n<p>📖 <a href=\"https://commitlint.js.org/#/\">@commitlint</a></p>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"참고\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0\" aria-label=\"참고 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\"